name: Feed a Family for the Week
description:
Please donate money to feed a family for a week in Roaring River, Jamaica.  Right now it's really difficult times for them as there are no tourists coming to the village.  A lot of the people go to bed hungry, or go even the whole day without food.  The exchange rate right now is 86 Jamaican dollars to one American dollar.  

Check out the blog!  http://lovejamaicalove.tumblr.com/

name: Feed a Family for a Month
description:
Please donate to feed a family well for a month in Roaring River, Jamaica.  Right now times are difficult as there are no tourists coming to the village.  A lot of people, young and old, in the village and all over the island go to bed hungry or go the whole day without food.  Have it in your heart to help them today.  Please feel free to contact Sarah (the founder of Jamaica Love) if you have any concerns or questions about the program. One Love♥ 

Check out the blog!  http://lovejamaicalove.tumblr.com/

name: Story Books
description:
Buy story books for the children at Roaring River Basic School in Westmoreland, Jamaica and surrounding schools.
Thank you for sending jamaica love♡

Check out the blog here!    http://lovejamaicalove.tumblr.com/

name: Swingset
description:
